RSS Feeds Agenda minutes What are RSS Feeds?

City of Rosemead meeting videos are arranged by date, with the most recent at the top of the list. Click View Event or In Progress to watch a live meeting. Click Video to watch an archived meeting with documents, or Agenda or Minutes to view the documents alone. You can also search the archives by typing keywords into the Search box.


To enable the most effective streaming experience for all browsers and operating systems, please download and install Silverlight from Microsoft.


The minimum system requirements for watching the Archived video are available here.
